{
  "stem": "4662.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, when we got up, we flew-- we ran down the street to the other cellar.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We ran over dead bodies as if it was bag-- bags of sand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't even notice they were dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we've got to the other cellar, it was the only cellar standing, and the people in still alive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we left as quick as you could leave, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And went on to the next town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think in the next town, we stayed for a while, until the Germans took over that town, and then we had to go back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With a cart-- horse and a cart, we went back to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't think of it like that because they only started with the Jewish people in 1942.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody stopped us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody said anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my husband earned a living with selling things from here to there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] With another friend of his.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we, we existed-- or just existed, trying to live, and tried to make the best of things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't really know what was going to happen in 1942, that we were all going to get caught and gassed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they kept that very, very secret.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there weren't any newspapers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There weren't any papers at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No-- we weren't allowed to have radios, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother-in-law?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she-- no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She lived-- they lived alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They lived in another apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She lived with my brother-in-law and his, and his baby.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived in our little house my mother gave us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When things changed, when we heard they're beginning with the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had a friend called Joss.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a salesman also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came over and helped us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
